data.title: 40 Acres of Land for Sale in Kasson, Minnesota
data.meta_description: This vacant residential 40-acre property for sale in Dodge County, MN could be the ideal location for your dream home. View this Kasson property today.
data.text: Attention developers and investors, don't miss your chance at this great property located just on the outskirts of the bustling community of Kasson, a town that consistently ranks in the top five safest places to live in Minnesota. Off a major highway, this property is ripe for development as it is in the highly sought-after school district of Kasson-Mantorville. This prime location allows residents to enjoy all the amenities this community has to offer along with an excellent education system! A mere 20 minutes west of Rochester on a four-lane highway, this location is in the "backyard" of the Word-Renowned Mayo Clinic. Furthermore, only a short hour to the Twin Cities, where one can catch the nightlife and concert venues that attract national artists.
